---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <article class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About Me</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-4">
      Hi! I'm a writer and developer sharing my thoughts and experiences through this blog.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      This blog is a space where I explore various topics ranging from technology to personal development.
      I believe in sharing knowledge and experiences that might help others on their journey.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      Feel free to reach out if you'd like to connect or collaborate on interesting projects.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>